<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Accès Activé | Trading IA</title>
    <style>
        body { background: #050505; color: white; font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; height: 100vh; margin: 0; }
        .card { background: rgba(0, 20, 30, 0.9); border: 2px solid #00f3ff; padding: 50px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 243, 255, 0.4); max-width: 400px; }
        h1 { color: #00f3ff; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        p { color: #00ff88; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 30px; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 15px 30px; background: #00f3ff; color: black; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase; transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn:hover { background: #fff; box-shadow: 0 0 20px #00f3ff; transform: scale(1.05); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
    <div style="font-size: 50px; margin-bottom: 20px;">✔️</div>
    <h1>ACCÈS ACTIVÉ</h1>
    <p>Identité vérifiée. Le terminal est prêt.</p>
    <a href="/login" class="btn">Accéder au Terminal</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>